@page
@using Web.Pages.Classes
@model Web.Pages.HomeModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Home";
    ViewData["ActivePage"] = BreadCrumbs.Home;

}
@*
    <h1 class="display-1 display-1">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>*@

<div class="container">
    <div class="jumbotron">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-3 profilePic">
                <img src="~/lib/images/tobiAtTesla.png" alt="tobiAtTesla.jpg" asp-append-version=true>

            </div>

            <div class="col-md-9 profileInfo">
                <h4 class="display-5">Kareem Oluwatobi</h4>
                <h6 class="fs-4">Developer | Writer | Entrepreneur</h6>
                <div class="floatingText">
                    <div class="carousel slide" id="carouselEx" data-bs-ride="carousel">
                        <div class="carousel-inner">
                            <div class="carousel-item active">
                                <p class="fs-5">... and a car enthusiast</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="carousel-item">
                                <p class="fs-5">... and a soccer player</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="carousel-item">
                                <p class="fs-5">... and a traveler</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="carousel-item">
                                <p class="fs-5">... and a food lover</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="carousel-item">
                                <p class="fs-5">... and a motivator</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <p class="fs-6"> I am a man of Fortune, And I must seek my Fortune</p>

                <div class="contactArea">
                    <ul class="social_footer_ul">
                        <li>
                            <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/oluwatobikareem/" target="_blank">
                                <i class="fab fa-linkedin"></i>
                            </a>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <a href="https://www.twitter.com/captainoath/" target="_blank">
                                <i class="fab fa-twitter"></i>
                            </a>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <a href="https://www.instagram.com/captainoath/" target="_blank">
                                <i class="fab fa-instagram"></i>
                            </a>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <a target="_self" asp-page="/Contact">
                                <i class="fab fa-telegram"></i>
                            </a>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="jumbotron">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4 profilePic">
                <h6 class="display-6">Catch What I am up to</h6>

                <div class="containAccord">
                    <div class="bg-blue"></div>

                    <div class="row rowstart">
                        <div class="col-12 border-bottom px-4 py-2">
                            <div class="row p-0 rowstart">
                                <div class=" col-md-2 d-flex justify-content-center">
                                    <img class="pic mb-md-0 mb-3"
                                         src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/373543/pexels-photo-373543.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&dpr=2&w=500"
                                         alt="">
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-md-10 ps-5">
                                    <p class="h-blue fs-6">... more like, what's on my mind.</p>
                                    <p class="textmuted fs-6">Give your suggestion and feel free to invite me to an event by clicking the plus icon below:</p>
                                    <div class="box d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mt-3">

                                        @{
                                            if (Model.IsTobiKareem)
                                            {
                                                <p class="">
                                                    <a role="button" class="mindfeed" asp-page="/CreatePost"><i class="fas fa-plus mindfeed"></i></a>
                                                </p>
                                            }
                                            else
                                            {
                                                <p class="">
                                                    <a role="button" class="mindfeed" asp-page="/Suggestions"><i class="fas fa-plus mindfeed"></i></a>
                                                </p>
                                            }
                                        }
                                        <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                                            <p class="textmuted">my weekly productivity score: 90%</p>
                                            <div class="progress-bar">
                                                <div data-size="" class="progress"></div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="col-12">

                            @{
                                foreach (var p in Model.DisplayPosts)
                                {
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="col-12">
                                            <div class="collapse show multi-collapse" id="multiCollapseExample1">
                                                <div class="border-bottom py-2">
                                                    <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                                                        <div>
                                                            <p class="p-blue">@p.Title</p>
                                                            <p class="textmuted">@Extend.GetTimeDifference(@p.CreatedOn)</p>
                                                        </div>
                                                        <div class="arrow">
                                                            @* <a role="button" class="mindfeed"> <i class="fas fa-thumbs-up"></i></a> *@
                                                            <a asp-page="/BlogPost" asp-route-id="@p.Id"><div class="btn btn-primary fas fa-arrow-right"></div> </a>
                                                        </div>
                                                    </div>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                }
                            }

                            <p class="hide">
                                <button class="btn btn-primary px-1" type="button"
                                        data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#multiCollapseExample1" aria-expanded="true"
                                        aria-controls="multiCollapseExample1">
                                    <p class="p-blue"><span class="fas fa-chevron-up pe-2"></span>Hide @Model.DisplayPosts.Count Units</p>
                                </button>
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>


            <div class="col-md-8 homeContents">

                <div class="aboutMe">
                    <h6 class="display-6">About Me</h6>
                    <p class="fs-6 lh-base">
                        I am a Full-Stack Software Developer, a Writer and an Entrepreneur. I am passionate about what I
                        do. My most recent work experience is at Tesla Inc. as a Senior Software Engineer.
                    </p>
                    <p class="fs-6 lh-base">
                        I am confident in my abilities to produce and my main strength is my leadership and ability to
                        engage in teamwork, which is evident in various team projects I have done on the job... <a asp-page="/About" class="m-1">Read more</a>
                    </p>
                    
                </div>

                <div class="developer">
                    <h6 class="display-6">Developer</h6>
                    <p class="fs-6 lh-base">
                        When I was 15 years old, my father bought a windows desktop and set it up at home. I was
                        fascinated by the way Microsoft Word works at the time. It was my first experience at typing.
                        It became even more fascinating that I could save the words and come back to it later.
                    </p>

                    <p class="fs-6 lh-base">
                        I can most likely say my love and habit for coding was a transition from the excitement at typing on Microsoft Word. The joyful experience became something that would change my life forever... <a asp-page="/Developer" class="m-1">Explore</a>
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="writer">
                    <h6 class="display-6">Writer</h6>
                    <p class="fs-6 lh-base">
                        I have a passion for writing. I love writing software codes, I love to write abstract stories,
                        copy writing, review writing and more specifically, poems.
                    </p>

                    <p class="fs-6 lh-base">
                        I love to use a lot of big words in my write ups to make me look and sound smart. Like utilizing gargantuan expressions for simple idioms.
                    </p>
                    
                    <p class="fs-6 lh-base">
                        If you have as much zeal or interest in writing, please consider creating a post on my website... <a asp-page="/Writer" class="m-1">Explore</a>
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="entrepreneur">
                    <h6 class="display-6">Entrepreneur</h6>
                    <p class="fs-6 lh-base">
                        In my college days, I had a desire to start a business. I was always interested in the idea of selling stuffs. My first business was selling shoes and flip flops.
                        Then selling edible plantain chips (popularly known as "Dodo Ikire"). Need I mention my profit margin was so great that it just became a thing of joy to make profit selling stuffs.
                    </p>

                    <p class="fs-6 lh-base">
                        I enjoyed being a sales man at the end, As I was often told, my charisma was a delight. And then, I boast to myself that, I can sell water to a well. 
                    </p>
                    
                    <p class="fs-6 lh-base">
                        Currently, My clique (called "Founding Fathers") and I operate a car renting business where we rent out luxury cars to people who need them. I also offer an introductory course
                        to programming and web development for a negotiable fee, (You may write me a review or read my reviews in the <a asp-page="/Writer" class="m-1">Writer</a> section and select Review on Category). To learn more, please contact me... <a asp-page="/Contact" class="m-1">Click Here</a>
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</div>
